summary: This document is a declaration by a custodian of records in response to a Grand Jury Subpoena issued on July 11, 2019, by Assistant United States Attorney Alex Rossmiller. It certifies the authenticity and proper maintenance of records requested by the subpoena, affirming that they were created in the regular course of business.

persons.name: Alex Rossmiller
persons.context: Alex Rossmiller is mentioned as the signatory of the Grand Jury Subpoena requesting records.

events.title: Grand Jury Subpoena Issued
events.description: A Grand Jury Subpoena was issued requesting specified records from a business.

keyFacts: The declaration is made under penalty of perjury.
The records were requested in a Grand Jury Subpoena dated July 11, 2019.
The custodian of records certifies the authenticity of the records provided.
